[38;5;141m> [0mI have all the context I need. Now I'll write the recipe for Chapter 8.1: Chief Complaint Classification. This is a "Simple" complexity recipe about classifying free-text chief complaints into standardized categories using traditional NLP (non-LLM) techniques.[0m[0m
